thread.title: Shirley

author: Shirley
title: Shirley
text:
Allan Ely at your Springwood Branch was very helpful, always welcome you with a smile and always by name. He made me feel very important.
He explained and answer everything that I asked,
He knew all about the different cars that I enquired about.
The other staff were great too all were smiling and helpful and also made you feel welcome.
I would recommend him and this company to anyone. I would also recommend the Holden Trax.
